sys_update_xml.payload:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update sys_domain="global" table="sn_cmp_rp_filter"><sn_cmp_rp_filter action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><name>GetRegionsForCloudAccount</name><resource_pool display_value="Location Pool">ddae1a84db7dc0902b72f6dc0c961978</resource_pool><script><![CDATA[getFilteredRecords(json);
//Do not remove function declaration
/** Input parameters
 * @param json - map for properties which you need to run this script
 * @returns filtered records in the format [{"value"="lookupValue",label="displayValue"}]
 */
function getFilteredRecords(json) {
	gs.info("@@@ the json is :"+json);
    var filteredRecords = [];
    if (json != null && json != "") {
        var map = new global.JSON().decode(json);
        var cloudAccount = map.CloudAccount;
		gs.info("@@@ cloudAccount is :"+cloudAccount);
        var caGr = new GlideRecord("cmdb_ci_cmp_cloud_account");
        caGr.addQuery("sys_id", cloudAccount);
        caGr.query();
        if (caGr.next()) {
            gs.info("@@@ the ca is :" + caGr.name);
            var gr = new GlideRecord("sn_cmp_ca_assc_datacenter");
            gr.addQuery("cloud_account", caGr.getUniqueValue());
            gr.addQuery("status", "1");
            gr.query();

            while (gr.hasNext()) {
                gr.next();
                gs.info("@@@ assc dc :" + gr.ldc_id.object_id);
				filteredRecords.push({"label": gr.ldc_id.object_id+"", "value": gr.ldc_id.object_id+"" });
            }
        }
    }
	gs.info("@@@ fl :"+new global.JSON().encode(filteredRecords));
    //force to string
    return new global.JSON().encode(filteredRecords);
}]]></script><sys_class_name>sn_cmp_rp_filter</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>admin</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2019-12-17 18:44:16</sys_created_on><sys_domain>global</sys_domain><sys_id>a71312d1db7548902b72f6dc0c96196a</sys_id><sys_mod_count>0</sys_mod_count><sys_name>GetRegionsForCloudAccount</sys_name><sys_package display_value="Cloud Management Platform" source="sn_cmp">80d50579eb203200979aa5115206fedd</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_scope display_value="Cloud Management Platform">80d50579eb203200979aa5115206fedd</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sn_cmp_rp_filter_a71312d1db7548902b72f6dc0c96196a</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>admin</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2019-12-17 18:44:16</sys_updated_on><type>script</type></sn_cmp_rp_filter></record_update>

sys_update_xml.payload:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update sys_domain="global" table="sn_cmp_rp_filter"><sn_cmp_rp_filter action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><name>GetLocationsForCloudAccount</name><resource_pool display_value="Location Pool">ddae1a84db7dc0902b72f6dc0c961978</resource_pool><script><![CDATA[getFilteredRecords(json);
//Do not remove function declaration
/** Input parameters
 * @param json - map for properties which you need to run this script
 * @returns filtered records in the format [{"value"="lookupValue",label="displayValue"}]
 */
function getFilteredRecords(json) {
	gs.info("@@@ the json is :"+json);
    var filteredRecords = [];
    if (json != null && json != "") {
        var map = new global.JSON().decode(json);
        var cloudAccount = map.CloudAccount;
		gs.info("@@@ cloudAccount is :"+cloudAccount);
        var caGr = new GlideRecord("cmdb_ci_cmp_cloud_account");
        caGr.addQuery("sys_id", cloudAccount);
        caGr.query();
        if (caGr.next()) {
            gs.info("@@@ the ca is :" + caGr.name);
            var gr = new GlideRecord("sn_cmp_ca_assc_datacenter");
            gr.addQuery("cloud_account", caGr.getUniqueValue());
            gr.addQuery("status", "1");
            gr.query();

            while (gr.hasNext()) {
                gr.next();
                gs.info("@@@ assc dc :" + gr.ldc_id.object_id);
				filteredRecords.push({"label": gr.alias+"", "value": gr.alias+"" });
            }
        }
    }
	gs.info("@@@ fl :"+new global.JSON().encode(filteredRecords));
    //force to string
    return new global.JSON().encode(filteredRecords);
}]]></script><sys_class_name>sn_cmp_rp_filter</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>admin</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2019-12-13 22:41:56</sys_created_on><sys_domain>global</sys_domain><sys_id>5a5f12c4db7dc0902b72f6dc0c9619f6</sys_id><sys_mod_count>15</sys_mod_count><sys_name>GetLocationsForCloudAccount</sys_name><sys_package display_value="Cloud Management Platform" source="sn_cmp">80d50579eb203200979aa5115206fedd</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_scope display_value="Cloud Management Platform">80d50579eb203200979aa5115206fedd</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sn_cmp_rp_filter_5a5f12c4db7dc0902b72f6dc0c9619f6</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>admin</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2019-12-17 19:55:32</sys_updated_on><type>script</type></sn_cmp_rp_filter></record_update>
